e and finance industries)</li>
<li>Applied information economics</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrostatistics" title=3D"Astr=
ostatistics">Astrostatistics</a> (statistical evaluation of astronomical da=
ta)</li>
