trics">Econometrics</a> (statistical analysis of economic data)</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistical_study_of_energy_da=
ta" title=3D"Statistical study of energy data">Energy statistics</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Engineering_statistics" title=
=3D"Engineering statistics">Engineering statistics</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Epidemiology" title=3D"Epidemi=
ology">Epidemiology</a> (statistical analysis of disease)</li>
