rmation_system" title=3D"Geographic information system">geographic informat=
ion systems</a>, specifically in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/S=
patial_analysis" title=3D"Spatial analysis">spatial analysis</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Image_processing" class=3D"mw-=
redirect" title=3D"Image processing">Image processing</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jurimetrics" title=3D"Jurimetr=
ics">Jurimetrics</a> (<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Law" title=
=3D"Law">law</a>)</li>
