 title=3D"Sabermetrics">sabermetrics</a> =E2=80=93 and <a href=3D"https://e=
n.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cricket_statistics" title=3D"Cricket statistics">crick=
et</a></li></ul></div>
<p>Statistics form a key basis tool in business and manufacturing as well. =
It is used to understand measurement systems variability, control processes=
 (as in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistical_process_contro=
